Earlier this year, we announced Microsoft Surface Laptop 6 for Business and Surface Pro 10 for Business, and the response has been incredible. Customers have been excited to explore the possibilities of how AI experiences can enhance productivity with the first Surface PCs optimized for AI and built with the new Copilot key. On top of that, we designed those devices to be packed with features that business customers have been requesting – including amazing performance with the latest Intel® Core™ Ultra processors, longer battery life, more ports, better security and innovative new anti-reflective displays. 

Today we’re announcing two new Copilot+ PCs: Surface Laptop, 7th Edition and Surface Pro, 11th Edition, the latest additions to our portfolio of devices available to our business customers. Built with the new Snapdragon® X Elite and Plus processors and Windows 11 Pro, these devices deliver the performance your teams need, are faster and have more AI acceleration than MacBook Airi. These new Copilot+ PCs with integrated NPU bring new AI experiences such as Recallii, Live Captions with Translationsiii, and new Windows Studio Effects help streamline everyday tasks, save valuable time and make it even easier to collaborate. 

Customers are excited about the potential that these new Copilot+ PCs can deliver including Deutsche Vermögensberatung (DVAG), Germany’s largest independent financial advisory service. 

We focus on delivering the best experiences to our advisors, and the new Surface Pro and Laptop with the Snapdragon X Series processors with its NPU capabilities can support our AI-driven workflows and our entire application landscape to take our efficiency to the next level.
– Christian Glanz, CIO, Deutsche Vermögensberatung (DVAG) 

The all-new Surface Laptop and Surface Pro are designed to revolutionize PC productivity and will be available alongside Surface Pro 10 and Surface Laptop 6. By adding to the diversity of hardware within the Surface portfolio, we’re giving customers more choice than ever before to choose the right devices that meet the unique needs of their organization. 

Surface Laptop, 7th Edition


The all-new Surface Laptop helps accelerate innovation, solve problems faster and drive business impact with new AI capabilities and Copilot experiences powered by the new Snapdragon X Elite and Snapdragon X Plus processors. 

Surface Laptop has been completely redesigned from the ground up to help teams be even more productive with stunning new brighter displays with razor thin bezels, more ports than ever before, faster connectivity with Wi-Fi 7iv, up to 22 hours of battery lifev and more.  Offered in two sizes, our 13.8” display provides larger viewing area than traditional 14”, in a more compact design and a 15” for expanded visuals now easier to carry around. 

The full HD Surface Studio Camera integrates perfectly with AI-powered Windows Studio Effects like Automatic Framing, Portrait Blur, Creative Filters and Eye Contact so your teams show up clearly and with confidence on all video calls with apps like Teams and Zoom.  Premium Omnisonic® Speakers coupled with AI-enhanced Studio Mics with Voice Focus amplify their voices and impact.   

The keyboard on Surface Laptop delivers an incredible typing experience with every keystroke perfected for comfort, speed and sound. The new haptic touchpad allows users to experience realistic feedback when tapped or clicked, have more control over their experience with adjustable pressure sensitivity, and supports intuitive touch gestures to make it easier to navigate. All of this is designed to empower all users to have more control over their mouse points with the most inclusive touchpad on the market. 

Offering ultimate protection from chip-to-cloud, Surface Laptop with the Microsoft Pluton security processor and TPM 2.0 is a Secured-core PC for the highest level of Windows PC protection. With Windows 11 Pro and Windows Hello Enhanced Sign-in Security (ESS) Surface Laptop provides unparalleled biometrics security you can trust.   

Surface Pro, 11th Edition

The all-new Surface Pro unlocks a new way to think about a laptop. Built with the new Snapdragon X Elite and Snapdragon X Plus processors, we’re delivering incredible performance that is 90% faster than Surface Pro 9. The integrated NPU delivers almost 20% more TOPS for AI processing than the Apple iPad Pro M4vi making it exceptionally well-suited for running multiple AI models simultaneously. It’s designed to empower teams that are always on-the-go with lightning-fast performance, AI-accelerated power and a stunning optional OLED display – all in a thin, light and versatile package.  

Surface Pro adapts to your teams’ needs through the day. When they are docked in at the office the new Surface Pro supports fast connectivity with Wi-Fi 7ii, and the ability to connect up to three 4k monitorsvii. When they are on the go, they can benefit from the blazing fast optional 5G connectionviii and up to 14 hours of battery lifeix – all designed to maximize productivity from anywhere.  

With the all-new Surface Pro Flex Keyboardx, we’re delivering even more versatility to create the perfect workstation wherever your team is working. Surface Pro Flex Keyboard is ready to be used attached to new Surface Pro, 11th Edition or Surface Pro 10 for the ultimate laptop set-up or detachedxi as a standalone keyboard for more flexibility. 

Whether your teams are dialing in from the road, the home office or the conference room, the view is crystal clear with the ultra-wide front facing camera paired with AI-enabled automatic framing to stay in frame. New enhanced voice focus exclusive to Copilot+ PCs leverages the power of the NPU to remove background noise for maximum clarity on video or audio calls and let the Studio Mics focus on your voice. 

Surface Pro is a Secured-Core PC with the Microsoft Pluton security processor and TPM 2.0 that offer top-notch security tailored for business needs. Zero-trust principles are designed into every layer of our chip-to-cloud security including Windows Hello for Business Enhanced Sign-in Security (ESS), enabled by default, which  protects  biometric data. The integrated NFC readerxii facilitates secure password-less authentication with greater ease when used with NFC security keys such as YubiKey 5C NFCvi.  

All this performance is wrapped up in an ultra-portable design that can replace your tablet, your laptop and making you more efficient, and more creative, all while keeping company data safe and secure.
